A demonstration dataset of European museums, artists, artworks, and exhibitions. This hub illustrates how
NeoWiki connects entities across schemas, similar to the cultural-heritage scenarios ECHOLOT and GLAM partners
work with. The data is curated for demonstration only and is not authoritative.

