== Which museums have the most visitors? ==

{{#invoke:NeoWikiDemo|query|MATCH (m:Museum) RETURN m.name AS Museum, m.`Annual visitors` AS `Annual visitors` ORDER BY `Annual visitors` DESC|columns=Museum, Annual visitors|linkColumns=Museum}}

== Browse ==

{{#invoke:NeoWikiDemo|query|MATCH (m:Museum)-[:`Located in`]->(c:City) RETURN m.name AS Museum, c.name AS City, m.Founded AS Founded, m.`Annual visitors` AS `Annual visitors` ORDER BY Museum|columns=Museum, City, Founded, Annual visitors|linkColumns=Museum, City}}

